[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "EAST OF THE SUN AND WEST OF THE MOON",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "They were all pretty, but the prettiest of all was the youngest daughter, who was so beautiful that there were no bounds to her beauty.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "The man went out to see what could be the matter, and when he got out there stood a great big white bear.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "\"Good evening,\" said the man.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "Truly the man would have had no objection to be rich, but he thought to himself: \"I must first ask my daughter about this,\" so he went in and told them that there was a great white bear outside who had faithfully promised to make them all rich if he might but have the youngest daughter.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "She said no, and would not hear of it; so the man went out again, and settled with the White Bear that he should come again next Thursday evening, and get her answer.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "Then the man persuaded her, and talked so much to her about the wealth that they would have, and what a good thing it would be for herself, that at last she made up her mind to go, and washed and mended all her rags, made herself as smart as she could, and held herself in readiness to set out.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "Little enough had she to take away with her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "Next Thursday evening the White Bear came to fetch her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "She seated herself on his back with her bundle, and thus they departed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "When they had gone a great part of the way, the White Bear said: \"Are you afraid?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "\"No, that I am not,\" said she.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "\"Keep tight hold of my fur, and then there is no danger,\" said he.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "The White Bear gave her a silver bell, and told her that when she needed anything she had but to ring this bell, and what she wanted would appear.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "So after she had eaten, and night was drawing near, she grew sleepy after her journey, and thought she would like to go to bed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "She rang the bell, and scarcely had she touched it before she found herself in a chamber where a bed stood ready made for her, which was as pretty as anyone could wish to sleep in.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000012_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000012_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "It had pillows of silk, and curtains of silk fringed with gold, and everything that was in the room was of gold or silver, but when she had lain down and put out the light a man came and lay down beside her, and behold it was the White Bear, who cast off the form of a beast during the night.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000012_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000012_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "She never saw him, however, for he always came after she had put out her light, and went away before daylight appeared.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "Then the White Bear asked what it was that she wanted, and she told him that it was so dull there in the mountain, and that she had to go about all alone, and that in her parents' house at home there were all her brothers and sisters, and it was because she could not go to them that she was so sorrowful.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "\"No, indeed,\" said she, \"I shall never forget;\" and as soon as she was at home the White Bear turned round and went back again.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "There were such rejoicings when she went in to her parents that it seemed as if they would never come to an end.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000018_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000018_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "Now they had everything that they wanted, and everything was as good as it could be.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000018_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000018_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "They all asked her how she was getting on where she was.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000018_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000018_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "All was well with her too, she said; and she had everything that she could want.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000018_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000018_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "What other answers she gave I cannot say, but I am pretty sure that they did not learn much from her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000018_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000018_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "But in the afternoon, after they had dined at midday, all happened just as the White Bear had said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000018_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000018_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "Her mother wanted to talk with her alone in her own chamber.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000018_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000018_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "But she remembered what the White Bear had said, and would on no account go. \"What we have to say can be said at any time,\" she answered.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000018_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000018_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "But somehow or other her mother at last persuaded her, and she was forced to tell the whole story.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000018_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000018_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "\"Oh!\" cried the mother, in horror, \"you are very likely sleeping with a troll!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000018_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000018_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "But I will teach you a way to see him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000018_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000018_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "You shall have a bit of one of my candles, which you can take away with you hidden in your breast.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "So she did kiss him; but while she was doing it she let three drops of hot tallow fall upon his shirt, and he awoke.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000019_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000019_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "If you had but held out for the space of one year I should have been free.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000019_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000019_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "I have a step mother who has bewitched me so that I am a white bear by day and a man by night; but now all is at an end between you and me, and I must leave you, and go to her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "She wept and lamented, but all in vain, for go he must.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "Then she asked him if she could not go with him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "But no, that could not be.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "\"Yes, you may do that,\" said he; \"but there is no way thither.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "It lies east of the sun and west of the moon, and never would you find your way there.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "When she awoke in the morning both the Prince and the castle were gone, and she was lying on a small green patch in the midst of a dark, thick wood.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000022_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000022_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "So when she had rubbed the sleep out of her eyes, and wept till she was weary, she set out on her way, and thus she walked for many and many a long day, until at last she came to a great mountain.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000022_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000022_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "Outside it an aged woman was sitting, playing with a golden apple.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000022_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000022_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "The girl asked her if she knew the way to the Prince who lived with his stepmother in the castle which lay east of the sun and west of the moon, and who was to marry a princess with a nose which was three ells long.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000022_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000022_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "\"How do you happen to know about him?\" inquired the old woman; \"maybe you are she who ought to have had him.\" \"Yes, indeed, I am,\" she said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000022_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000022_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "You will be a long time in getting to it, if ever you get to it at all; but you shall have the loan of my horse, and then you can ride on it to an old woman who is a neighbor of mine: perhaps she can tell you about him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000022_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000022_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "When you have got there you must just strike the horse beneath the left ear and bid it go home again; but you may take the golden apple with you.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "So the girl seated herself on the horse, and rode for a long, long way, and at last she came to the mountain, where an aged woman was sitting outside with a gold carding comb.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "So she did this, and journeyed to the South Wind, neither was she very long on the way.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000026_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000026_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "If you like, however, I will go with you to my brother, the North Wind; he is the oldest and strongest of all of us, and if he does not know where it is no one in the whole world will be able to tell you.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000026_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000026_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "You may sit upon my back, and then I will carry you there.\" So she seated herself on his back, and off he went from his house in great haste, and they were not long on the way.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000026_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000026_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "\"What do you want?\" he roared out from afar, and they froze as they heard.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "\"Yes,\" said the North Wind, \"I know where it is.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000027_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000027_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "However, if you really are anxious to go there, and are not afraid to go with me, I will take you on my back, and try if I can blow you there.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "\"Get there I must,\" said she; \"and if there is any way of going I will; and I have no fear, no matter how fast you go.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "Down below there was such a storm!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000030_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000030_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "It blew down woods and houses, and when they were above the sea the ships were wrecked by hundreds.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000030_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000030_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "\"Art thou afraid?\" said the North Wind.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000030_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000030_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "\"I have no fear,\" said she; and it was true.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "\"How much do you want for that gold apple of yours, girl?\" said she, opening the window.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000031_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000031_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "\"It can't be bought either for gold or money,\" answered the girl.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000031_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000031_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "\"If it cannot be bought either for gold or money, what will buy it?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000031_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000031_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "You may say what you please,\" said the Princess.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000032_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000032_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "In the daytime she sat down once more beneath the windows of the castle, and began to card with her golden carding comb; and then all happened as it had happened before.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000032_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000032_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "The Princess asked her what she wanted for it, and she replied that it was not for sale, either for gold or money, but that if she could get leave to go to the Prince, and be with him during the night, she should have it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000032_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000032_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "But when she went up to the Prince's room he was again asleep, and, let her call him, or shake him, or weep as she would, he still slept on, and she could not put any life in him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000032_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000032_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "So she opened the window, and asked what she would take for it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000032_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000032_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "The girl said what she had said on each of the former occasions-that it was not for sale either for gold or for money, but if she could get leave to go to the Prince who lived there, and be with him during the night, she should have it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "\"Yes,\" said the Princess, \"I will gladly consent to that.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000034_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000034_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "I will say that I want to see what my bride can do, and bid her wash the shirt which has the three drops of tallow on it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "If she cannot do that, she is not worth having.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "So the other trolls had to come and wash, but, the more they did, the blacker and uglier grew the shirt, until at length it was as black as if it had been up the chimney.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000037_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1168/134958/1168_134958_000037_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1168",
        "content": "There is a beggar girl sitting outside the window, and I'll be bound that she can wash better than any of you!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1168_134958_000037_000003",
